<p>It's not the first time an X-rated joke has made its way onto The Block this year.</p>

<p>In an episode earlier this month, The Block's resident foreman Keith Schleiger asked George Bragias if he had 'trouble getting it up' after noticing the contestant's ceiling rose lying on the floor.</p>

<p>Naughty boy: At one stage, their design took on a phallic shape, with a cheeky Jimmy, 33, leaning down and putting his mouth near the tip of the clay</p>

<p>While it took the 33-year-old electrician a moment to register what Keith had actually meant by the comment, he was left red-faced by the raunchy remark. </p>

<p>'We're gonna need six, seven guys to get this, so it's going to have to stay here at least so I can try and get it up,' George explained.</p>

<p>Without missing a beat, Keith asked: 'Do you have trouble getting it up?'</p>

